NAME
    Games::SolarConflict - Spacewar! clone

VERSION
    version 0.000001

DESCRIPTION
    Games::SolarConflict is a Spacewar! clone.

    This game was originally created for The SDL Perl Game Contest!

ATTRIBUTION
    The font and image files contained in this distribution are licensed
    separately from the code.

    *   UbuntuMono-BI.ttf

        Created by Canonical Ltd. <http://www.canonical.com/> and licensed
        under the Ubuntu Font License Version 1.0
        <http://font.ubuntu.com/licence/>, available at
        <http://font.ubuntu.com/>.

    *   backgound.bmp

        Based on spacefield_a-000.png
        <http://opengameart.org/sites/all/modules/pubdlcnt/pubdlcnt.php?file
        =http://opengameart.org/sites/default/files/spacefield_a-000.png&nid
        =3470> created by beren77 <http://opengameart.org/user/453> and
        licensed under the Public Domain, available at
        <http://opengameart.org/content/space-backdrop>.

    *   explosion.bmp

        Based on an image from jswars_gfx_cc3.zip
        <http://opengameart.org/sites/all/modules/pubdlcnt/pubdlcnt.php?file
        =http://opengameart.org/sites/default/files/jswars_gfx_cc3.zip&nid=3
        282> created by Jonas Wagner <http://29a.ch/> and licensed under
        CC-BY-SA 3.0
        <http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/legalcode>, available
        at
        <http://opengameart.org/content/asteroid-explosions-rocket-mine-and-
        laser>.

    *   spaceship1.bmp and spaceship2.bmp

        Based on ship360_32.png
        <http://opengameart.org/sites/all/modules/pubdlcnt/pubdlcnt.php?file
        =http://opengameart.org/sites/default/files/ship360_32.png&nid=4883>
        created by Killy Overdrive <http://www.killyoverdrive.co.cc/> and
        licensed under CC-BY 3.0
        <http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/legalcode>, available at
        <http://opengameart.org/content/spaceship-360>.

    *   sun.bmp

        Based on sun.png
        <http://opengameart.org/sites/all/modules/pubdlcnt/pubdlcnt.php?file
        =http://opengameart.org/sites/default/files/sun.png&nid=3568>
        created by NASA, Solar Dynamics Observatory
        <http://sdo.gsfc.nasa.gov/> and licensed under the Public Domain,
        available at <http://opengameart.org/content/the-sun>.

